# Verification Checklist

End every task with an explicit checklist. Do not say "done" — state the actual results.

Tailor to what was built. Omit items that don't apply; add specific ones that do.

```
## Verification
- [ ] pnpm run build — zero TypeScript errors
- [ ] pnpm run lint — zero ESLint/Prettier errors
- [ ] [specific endpoint] manually verified: GET /api/v1/health → 200 { status: ok }
- [ ] No unintended scope creep (list adjacent changes if any)
- [ ] No new npm packages added without flagging
- [ ] Soft delete filter present on all queries touching bookings/users (if schema changed)
- [ ] 2dsphere index defined alongside any new geo field (if schema changed)
- [ ] GeoJSON coordinates in [longitude, latitude] order (if geo field added)
- [ ] No feature/business logic added if task was "setup" or "scaffolding" only
```

If something failed, say so explicitly — do not mark it complete.
